name: Princess Castle Birthday Invite / Set of 10
description:
Every little girl is a princess in her own unique way! Why not celebrate her birthday by throwing her a princess themed birthday party! These invitations are printed on 5" x 7" heavy matte paper and include tropical green colored envelopes to match! **if you'd like to modify the colors, please email me and let me know! I will be more then happy to accommodate :) ** 

A digital proof will be e-mailed to you within 3 business days from when you place your order. As soon as your approve the proof, your order will printed and sent out asap!

There is a minimum quantity of 10 and this product is sold in increments of 10. If you would like to order more please adjust the quantity in your cart.

Also, if you would like to print these princess invitations yourself please add the DIY option to your cart!!

Thank you & Happy Shopping :)

name: Girl Owl Baby Shower Invite
description:
A modern and simple owl themed baby shower invitation to catch all your guests attention! Printed on off white 5" x 7" heavy weight matte paper and includes a 3.5" x 2.5" wishing well / registry card & a coral colored A7 envelope to match the flowers in the invitation. Please contact me if you'd like to customize the colors of this invitation, I will be happy to work with you!

A digital proof will be e-mailed to you within 3 business days from when you place your order. As soon as your approve the proof, your order will printed and sent out asap!

There is a minimum quantity of 25 and if you would like to order more then 100 invitations please contact me for pricing!

Please remember once you place the order, please contact me by email with all the information you would like on your invitations (such as mommy's name, date/time/place, RSVP info, "given by...", registry info, etc...) 

Thank you :)
